        },
        {
            "id": "6",
            "sentence": "يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ إِنَّكَ كَادِحٌ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ كَدْحًا فَمُلَـٰقِيهِ",
            "translation": "O humanity! Indeed, you are labouring restlessly towards your Lord, and will ˹eventually˺ meet the consequences.",
            "originals": [
